posting_body: ['Schedule a Tour Today: <URL>', 'Discover a life of ease at Palmetto Promenade.', 'At our luxury apartments in Boca Raton, residents will find a selection of one bedroom, two bedroom, and three bedroom homes that are sure to suit any lifestyle.', 'In each home, residents will enjoy the chef-caliber kitchens with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances, private balconies, and spacious closets with built-in shelving.', 'Throughout the community at our Boca apartments, residents can take advantage of the resort-style swimming pool with private cabanas, cutting-edge fitness center, and the outdoor entertainment area.', 'Amenities:', '-Gas ranges in Estate and Penthouse collection residences', '-Porcelain tile tub and shower surrounds', '-Designer lighting and plumbing fixtures', '-Walk-out balconies and large terraces available', "-Spacious 9' ceilings", '-Modern one, two and three bedroom residences', '-51-bottle wine cooler in most residences', '-Electric car charging stations', '-Wi-Fi access throughout residential amenities', '-Whirlpool appliance package including French door with bottom freezer in stainless steel refrigerator', '-Powder rooms in select residences', '-Resort-style landscaping and water features surround the community', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
